subject: Container setup
description:
As a developer, I want to deploy my code into a container so that it is easy for me to share my code and can interact with other microservices without much friction.

Definition of Done:

    Deploy the code into a container.

Acceptance criteria:

    Write a dockerfile for the project
    Build a docker image using the docker file
